net.rim.device.api.crypto
Interface SymmetricCryptoToken

All Superinterfaces:
CryptoToken, Persistable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AESCryptoToken, CAST128CryptoToken, DESCryptoToken, HMACCryptoToken, RC2CryptoToken, RC5CryptoToken, SkipjackCryptoToken, TripleDESCryptoToken
public interface SymmetricCryptoToken
extends CryptoToken

Defines a crypto token for symmetric key algorithms.

Crypto tokens are used to store and distribute crypotgraphic information.

Category:
Signed: This element is only accessible by signed applications. If you intend to use this element, please visit http://www.blackberry.com/go/codesigning to obtain a set of code signing keys. Code signing is only required for applications running on BlackBerry smartphones; development on BlackBerry Smartphone Simulators can occur without code signing.
Since:
BlackBerry API 3.6.0
